{"tid":2268716,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朴智宣與母陳屍家中 母親遺書曝光：我不能讓女兒一個人走","createTime":"2020-11-03T04:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T04:24:09.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0b3ad2e58b9334e1bca2181af770c3e63035663f","tid":2268716,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"據悉，朴智宣生前一直飽受陽光過敏的皮膚病的困擾，所以就算做了藝人亦以素顏出鏡，成為其特色。不過有消息指，朴智宣最近病情惡化，不論在戶外拍攝還是舞台燈光，都令她感到相當痛苦。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日在現場發現疑似朴智宣母親寫下的遺書，韓媒《朝鮮日報》將內容曝光：「女兒因皮膚病而非常痛苦，最近在治療其他疾病的過程中，令皮膚病更加惡化，亦感到更加痛苦。我不能讓女兒一個人走，老公對不起。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201103/KMU3RL6FR5EJNNIDU53GQLVBA4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201103%2FKMU3RL6FR5EJNNIDU53GQLVBA4%2F&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EmbkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=f066a6dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201103%2FKMU3RL6FR5EJNNIDU53GQLVBA4%2F&h=1b6851c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201103/KMU3RL6FR5EJNNIDU53GQLVBA4/</a>"},{"pid":"7fe02b65978fffae0c5f74c6086e9629295f5710","tid":2268716,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:24:09.000Z","msg":"韓國咁多cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}